text: JAG or Jag may refer to: * JAG (TV series), an American adventure/legal drama television series * Jag, nickname for Jaguar Cars * Jags, nickname for the Jacksonville Jaguars ==People== * James A. Garfield (1831-1881), 20th U.S. president * Michael Jagmin (born 1985), American rock singer ==Related pages==
